# ============================================================================
# FORMAT: [DOMAIN][SCOPE][COMPONENT][ACTION] TICKET-XXX: Summary
# ============================================================================
#
# DOMAIN (required) - What area of the codebase:
#   API      - Backend endpoints, routes, middleware
#   UI       - React components, client-side code, styles
#   NETWORK  - Network utilities, fetch, DNS, connections
#   SECURITY - Auth, secrets, validation, permissions
#   CONFIG   - Config files, bunfig, tsconfig, env
#   ADAPTER  - External integrations (S3, Redis, DB drivers)
#   MATRIX   - Analytics dashboards, monitoring views
#   PTY      - Terminal, pseudo-terminal, shell handling
#   UTILS    - Shared utilities and helpers
#   CORE     - Core infrastructure, types, base classes
#   DB       - Database schemas, queries, migrations
#   SCRIPT   - Build scripts, CLI tools, automation
#   TEST     - Test files, fixtures, mocks
#   DOCS     - Documentation only changes
#
# SCOPE (required) - What type of component:
#   ENDPOINT   - API endpoints
#   TAB        - Dashboard tabs/views
#   QUERY      - Database queries
#   ROUTER     - Routing logic
#   HANDLER    - Request/event handlers
#   VALIDATOR  - Input validation
#   MATRIX     - Matrix/grid components
#   UTILS      - Utility functions
#   CORE       - Core modules
#   HOOK       - React hooks
#   COMPONENT  - React components
#   SERVICE    - Backend services
#   MODEL      - Data models
#   BENCH      - Benchmarks
#   FIXTURE    - Test fixtures
#
# COMPONENT - Free-form module/file name (optional but recommended)
#
# ACTION (required) - What was done:
#   ADD      - New feature or file
#   FIX      - Bug fix
#   REFACTOR - Code restructuring (no behavior change)
#   OPTIMIZE - Performance improvement
#   REMOVE   - Deletion of feature or file
#   UPDATE   - Modification to existing feature
#   TEST     - Adding or updating tests
#   CHORE    - Maintenance tasks
#   DOCS     - Documentation updates
#   STYLE    - Formatting, whitespace changes
#   SECURITY - Security-related changes
#
# TICKET - Required. Format: [A-Z]+-[0-9]+ (e.g., ONE-123, GH-456, DASH-789)
#
# ============================================================================

